title: David Fisher - ModelMania Volumes Four & Five
description:
David Fisher - ModelMania Volumes One, Two & Three.
Resin and vinyl modeling and customizing, with David Fisher.
Whether you're a beginner or an experienced modeler, this DVD will arm you with the knowledge you need to turn your model kits into one-of-a-kind works of art. Enjoy it. This it is the second DVD. The third has not been created. We hope that they publish another one. I will upload more model building stuff. Greetings.
